article.description: — Alex Timmerman's 15 points helped Bucknell defeat Merrimack 61-55 on Sunday.
article.headline: Timmerman leads Bucknell to 61-55 victory over Merrimack
article.linkText: Timmerman leads Bucknell to 61-55 victory over Merrimack
article.story:
LEWISBURG, Pa. -- — Alex Timmerman's 15 points helped Bucknell defeat Merrimack 61-55 on Sunday.

Timmerman added five rebounds for the Bison (7-4). Xander Rice scored 11 points with nine assists.

Ziggy Reid finished with 20 points, two steals and two blocks for the Warriors (2-12). Jordan Minor added nine points, five steals and eight blocks.

------
